      "rationale": "The construct undergoes large-displacement bending with local yielding at the screw-rod interface. A nonlinear geometry (NLGEOM) formulation with bilinear isotropic hardening for Ti-6Al-4V is physically appropriate. Sensitivity analysis confirmed negligible difference between elastic and elastic-plastic predictions below yield, validating the model form choice."
