      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.1 GPa) derived from tensile coupon tests on the same material heat lot as the test constructs. Screw and rod geometry inputs verified against CMM measurements with tolerance < 0.02 mm. Uncertainty in material inputs propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000); coefficient of variation on stiffness QoI = 3.1%."
