      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-lot non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws and 5.5 mm rods. All components inspected per DePuy Synthes incoming inspection protocol. Dimensional records confirm components within drawing tolerances. Sample size provides sufficient statistical power for E/uval metric."
