      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading rates and environmental conditions, or single condition justified by insensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) in ambient laboratory conditions per ASTM F1717. Clinical loading is also quasi-static for this application; however, only one test condition was evaluated. Rate sensitivity analysis was not performed. Achieved level is 2 (single condition, no sensitivity analysis), below the required level of 3. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the quasi-static nature of the intended use."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
