      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably equivalent to test specimen and test fixture conditions.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry: inferior block fixed, superior block displaced axially at 10° offset. Fixture stiffness characterized experimentally and incorporated as a spring element. Material inputs matched to coupon test data from same lot. Equivalency confirmed by sensitivity analysis showing < 2% QoI change for ±5% variation in fixture stiffness."
    },
    {
