    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework demonstrates sufficient credibility for the stated COU. All 13 V&V 40 factors were assessed; 12 of 13 met or exceeded required levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the quasi-static nature of the loading and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96 and < 10% difference). The package conforms to ProfileMinimal; a digital signature has not yet been applied pending completion of the institutional signature workflow, but the sha256 hash provides content integrity verification in the interim.",
